flowchart TD

A[User Query]

A --> B[Vector Search]

B --> C[Select Top Sections]

C --> D{Cross-Doc References?}

D -->|Yes| E[Expand Context]
D -->|No| F[Skip Expansion]

E --> G[Assemble Context]
F --> G

G --> H{Enough Context?}

H -->|No| I[Retrieve More]
I --> B

H -->|Yes| J[Send to LLM]

